>create your pakage always inside a src directory of catkin_ws
to create a pakage :
~/catkin_ws/src$catkin_create_pkg pkg_name

pakage folder contains :
launch floder (.launch files)
src folder (c++,py files)
cmakelist.txt (list of cmake rules)
package.xml (package information and dependences)



>whenever you create a pakage ,you have to compile it in order to make your package work;
 compile pakage using :
 ~/catkin_ws$ catkin_make
 
 it is done inside a catkin_ws directory




